## 30 September 2023

### Service guide created

The service guide is a high-level overview and reference guide for the new RESTful EMCS API.

#### Additions

* A migration page with guidance for users who have previously used the old SOAP EMCS API.
* Pages describing each endpoint.
* Links to the API specification, testing guide, technical interface specification and changelogs.
* An 'Endpoint delivery status' page with information on expected and actual delivery dates for testing each endpoint.
* A brief glossary
* Information on getting started using the EMCS API for the first time
* Information on using the Developer Hub
* A high level process flow diagram

#### What impact does this have?

The service guide now provides a high-level overview of the API and relevant documentation, to support you in enabling your software to connect to the API.
